{
    "text": "The @everaftergarden will open in Grosvenor Square, Mayfair from 16 November to 19 December.   You can sponsor one of the garden\u2019s 25,000 roses in memory of a loved one. Funds raised go to cancer charity @royalmarsden   Open daily between 3pm - 9pm Free entry \u00a310 suggested minimum donation to dedicate a rose  #londonchristmas #christmasinlondon #royalmarsden #letsdolondon #londonforyou #londonbylondoners #londonlife #lovelondon #festivelondon #visitlondon #becauseimalondoner #londonweek #londonweekend #londontourist #londontourism #londontrip #londonblogger #londonbloggers #londondiaries #londonholiday #beautifullondon #discoverlondon #explorelondon #seelondon #londonart #artinlondon #thingstodoinlondon",
